├── BMR: 1,847 cal/day (calories burned at complete rest)
├── TDEE: 2,540 cal/day (BMR × 1.375 for lightly active)
├── Goal: Fat loss (moderate)
├── Target: 2,040 cal/day (500 cal deficit)
└── Expected rate: ~1 lb/week (varies ±0.5 lb)
```

